	<div class="section">
		<h2 class="section-heading">Education</h2>
		<div class="item">
			<div class="item-title">
				<span class="primary">MISIS University</span>
				<span class="secondary">Computer Science & Engineering</span>
			</div>
			<div class="meta">2025-2029 | Moscow, Russia</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="section">
		<h2 class="section-heading">About Me</h2>
		<div class="item">
			<p class="description">
				Focused on low-level and practical software development.
				Frequently experiment with various technologies and languages.
